I have done my fair share of ranting on here but not all my posts are negative.  I can give you plenty of PvE advice but I'm basically clueless how to stay alive in RvR.  One thing to keep in mind in PvE is that the high level confusions are a get out of death free card for any extra mobs that come in that are either too injured to be mezzed or that some stupid tank decides to whack on instead of the main /assist warrior.  They port around and sometimes hit their own kind but even if their own kind join in they do not aggro your group unless you attack them.<P>--------------------<P>May fate spare your soul another eve.  Terrak Thel is the beginning and the end.
