<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
As the other have said, a lot of the strategy discussion happened already. I hope the current discussions aren't too discouraging to new sorcerers. I would encourage you new sorcs or old sorcs who are new to the board to post your questions. Just because we all bitch and moan  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"> doesn't mean we don't help out. Every post asking for tips and help have gotten a lot of replied pretty quickly.<P>The pve strategy is fairly simple since the matter line is little used, so the two options are body (single target mez, then nuke) or mind (aoe mez, then lifetap). The rvr strategy is everchanging with each new patch, and I for one don't really enjoy aiming at a moving target like that while trying to figure out how to play. I still have flashbacks of doing that as a bard in everquest.  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>--Winin
